2. Install: `cargo install --path .`
3. Verify auto-filter: `rtk proxy -f pnpm build` in a project with build output вЂ” should show improved savings
4. Verify cache: run `rtk proxy -f cargo test` twice within 5 minutes вЂ” second run should show diff
5. Verify repeat hint: run `rtk cargo test` 3+ times in a row вЂ” should see stderr hint on 3rd run
6. Verify `RTK_CACHE=0 rtk proxy -f cargo test` вЂ” should show full output (cache disabled)
7. Verify `RTK_QUIET=1 rtk cargo test` вЂ” should not show repeat hint

